Package org.cast.cwm.xml

Interface Summary
ICacheableModel<T> A Model that can be used for caching derived objects.
IDocumentObserver Interface for classes that want to be notified when a document object is created or updated.
IXmlPointer A wrapper for an Element that uses a #getTransformer() to run an XSLT transform on XML content.
 

Class Summary
DomCache A cache of TransformResult objects.
DomCache.DOMKey A key composed of the model (which uniquely points to some XML) and the registered name of the transformer.
FileResource  
TransformResult Holds both the Element and serialized String form of the result of a transformation.
XmlDocument A class that parses and holds the high level structure of an XML document.
XmlDocumentList An ordered list of XmlDocument objects.
XmlSection Represents a section of an XML document.
XmlSectionModel A Model pointing to an XmlSection.
